Revision history for RPi-Radar-RCWL0516

0.01 UNREL
    - Auto generated distribution with Dist::Mgr
    - Added the OO Perl interface; pure Perl, with the GPIO transport
      provided by RPi::Pin, loaded at runtime so non-Pi machines can
      install and test the distribution
    - Added motion(), wait_for_motion(), wait_for_clear(), poll() and pin()
    - Added hardware-free parameter validation and mocked logic test suites
    - Added examples/motion_poll.pl and examples/motion_interrupt.pl
    - Added the TECHNICAL INFORMATION POD section with the RCWL-0516
      datasheet specifications, pinout and wiring, output timing and
      adjustment pad details
